{"hash":"3f23f5d40c100db3523bba4050340d17c40dacb9","data":{"post":{"title":"Diving Into Design Research","content":"<p>Today, the shift from traditional media to digital is inevitable in different industries such as health, government, real estate, and education. As these industries undergo digital transformations, the need to create new digital solutions and products that are intuitive, usable, and human-centered is increasing.Along with this change and demand brings about the relevance of Design Reserch.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 2560 1920' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-38fab8cfcab58248adff55ad080b5487'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-38fab8cfcab58248adff55ad080b5487)' width='2560' height='1920' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2b0gKTtrWOROBsrN9ObeeQZbIUgE7G5Nh3eOJCqNluOltufxBpa1oQUpRCQ5KKd7i2hA/fGb8jKLjjjgezVVNWraNTOgSdVvzOKHZ1jCOXTN8B%2b1UZJz3S/gBUnPlTaq3BerymVa06LXsRcpdT245oddeEJczQVMJdS1cdaiCbegxVZ2afiMmzcrUWgPx48kK/GqNRbU4CVAk6EA9g2J68LPDuHHceoLM1LbocrqWZEZ1sEA6Smxvz5jA5GsGS3fClskgw1x90hmoskKCwsW/TyxnErZbmtyVOjpGBpjgp%2bVkfcB919/THWFdyZl1uO0UUKnHUSFWji/K9tuXjyGBy%2bG%2bVXSC7RYh1cilRHpa2KS%2bJ2NNrJDWytzqvf1UV4cZejVeDNfmIeWG3UthKXVISoFNyDpIvvbnjxhUmM4oN0%2blNKSSNXwxdVt3rP%2bsPXBalPIyxMLiPqmE877BCcBf5W1V%2bbIclT2WGlrWUpSpSzpKttgAOXfjao%2bnILpcjZY0/N1aWm1kENTajosmQ4E9QbCGk%2bWkD98DX63H3sgOntWpTh9ycP0XhbTQEqly5TxuSQjSgHe/ecGomSqDBsWac0pY/M7dw%2b%2bGdbSRdkdyqemkd3vKkLNcnLeR8DEU5Y/QhFrjyw%2b0ymn4hFYhw3VPsLanqj9JoWp1s7EpI7DZQ67DDcqI20nQ0hKE9iRYe2BikyIUxD8VRQ7qTpX9vzAk9%2bwI88Aq6sVJBLALJlLAIsNKZY2dUVqlNvudE230mlYDnRKZUQQAtR5A7G/Lax54Nx6/R30Mlqp04q/TKbF7jnbVt4YiXFWqUimVmosRHm5KXjZbEZf0A8xcbDw37xiWz6TTktsOwnWnm3QToKSHGrcgva1z1WJ8sZ00LWN1jA9N/v4WhFI57tP8%2bvldR8HY9snrWd9Upz2CRhplxxzAxL8p8QqflfKSYbkGZLmJdWsIb0pSQbW%2bYnb0wBrHFjM1QKkU6FApjR5KVd9z3sPbEwVULIGguzZUTUc8lQ8huLqrrQElfYCcKteznQKQstSp6FyBv0TA6RXtsMSGoTKpV1FdYq0yWD%2bQuaUf4iwxrNxWGB%2bE2hPgMEk4izyi6ZFwx3nKeqjxIbWP6XSpDp%2b%2bQoNpHkLk4U67m/ME1gpU8xGZP1NR2/qHYVHf0tjUJ2sMar%2blbagSDgwrpS64wmChiaLWuhkxoPspWi2/UBgYLxUKbfWABunUd/DBRSbxlHWpKGRdSUgC%2b/b34GOsMrZJs2XVeenHTvDaqJrjuLrnWudSylo2X//2Q==' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"2560\" alt=\"alt text\" data-srcset=\"/cheannecruz/assets/static/design-research.82a2fbd.865bb1985b50c7aefb02d96422ca19dd.jpg 480w, /cheannecruz/assets/static/design-research.cbab2cf.865bb1985b50c7aefb02d96422ca19dd.jpg 1024w, /cheannecruz/assets/static/design-research.2665e34.865bb1985b50c7aefb02d96422ca19dd.jpg 1920w, /cheannecruz/assets/static/design-research.42db587.865bb1985b50c7aefb02d96422ca19dd.jpg 2560w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" data-src=\"/cheannecruz/assets/static/design-research.42db587.865bb1985b50c7aefb02d96422ca19dd.jpg\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/cheannecruz/assets/static/design-research.42db587.865bb1985b50c7aefb02d96422ca19dd.jpg\" width=\"2560\" alt=\"alt text\"></noscript></p>\n<p>Design research is foundational to creating products, services, and systems that respond to human needs. It is a crucial step in creating optimal user experience. It allows you to understand complex human behavior and turn that into actionable insights to improve your design.</p>\n<p>By conducting design research you will be able to learn more about your users or customers, and it will help you answer these questions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Who are your users or customers?</li>\n<li>What are their pain-points or problems they are facing?</li>\n<li>How will they use your product or service?</li>\n</ul>\n","mainBannerImage":"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1aISfyfarquXkvEq_saoo8ppoEJlJfqy0","dateCreated":"2020-05-21T00:00:00.000Z"}},"context":{}}